request.description:
First call after scanning a QR code. Now returns a `currency_info` block so the frontend can set up the currency selector before loading the menu.

**Query:** `t` (JWT token, required)

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "merchant_id": 5,
  "merchant_name": "My Restaurant",
  "merchant_logo": "https://...",
  "hexa_color_1": "#FF5733",
  "hexa_color_2": "#C70039",
  "branch_id": 3,
  "branch_name": "Downtown",
  "table_id": 7,
  "table_name": "12",
  "menus": [ { "id": 1, "name_ar": "القائمة", "name_en": "Menu", ... } ],
  "currency_info": {
    "base_currency": { "id": 1, "code": "EGP", "symbol": "ج.م", "name": "Egyptian Pound" },
    "default_display_currency": { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$", "name": "US Dollar" },
    "default_display_rate": 0.021,
    "available_currencies": [
      {
        "currency_id": 2,
        "rate_from_base": 0.021,
        "is_default_display": true,
        "currency": { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$", "name": "US Dollar" }
      },
      {
        "currency_id": 3,
        "rate_from_base": 0.019,
        "is_default_display": false,
        "currency": { "id": 3, "code": "EUR", "symbol": "€", "name": "Euro" }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Full menu with categories, items, variants and modifier groups. Each price field now has both a `base_price` (real DB value) and a `display_price` (converted). A `currency_info` block is always included.

**Query params:**
- `t` (JWT, required)
- `currency_id` (int, optional) — the display currency the customer selected. Falls back to merchant default if omitted or invalid.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "menu": { "id": 1, "name_ar": "...", "name_en": "..." },
  "currency_info": {
    "base_currency":         { "id": 1, "code": "EGP", "symbol": "ج.م" },
    "display_currency":      { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$" },
    "display_rate":          0.021,
    "default_display_currency": { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$" },
    "available_currencies": [ ... ]
  },
  "categories": [
    {
      "id": 10, "name_en": "Burgers",
      "items": [
        {
          "id": 100,
          "name_en": "Classic Burger",
          "base_price": 150,
          "display_price": 3.15,
          "base_currency":    { "id": 1, "code": "EGP", "symbol": "ج.م" },
          "display_currency": { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$" },
          "images": { "img_url_1": "https://...", "img_url_2": null },
          "variants": [
            { "id": 201, "name": "Large", "price": 180, "display_price": 3.78 }
          ],
          "modifier_groups": [
            {
              "group": { "id": 50, "name_en": "Extras" },
              "rule": { "min_select": 0, "max_select": 3 },
              "modifiers": [
                { "id": 301, "name_en": "Extra Cheese", "price": 20, "display_price": 0.42 }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

Validate a cart before checkout. Now accepts `currency_id` and returns display prices alongside base prices.

**Body:**
```json
{
  "merchant_id": 5,
  "branch_id": 3,
  "table_id": 7,
  "currency_id": 2,
  "items": [
    { "item_id": 100, "variant_id": null, "quantity": 2, "modifiers": [{ "modifier_id": 301, "quantity": 1 }] }
  ]
}
```
- `currency_id` (int, optional) — the display currency. Falls back to merchant default if omitted.

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "is_valid": true,
  "errors": [],
  "totals": {
    "subtotal": 320,
    "total": 320,
    "display_subtotal": 6.72,
    "display_total": 6.72
  },
  "currency_info": {
    "display_currency": { "id": 2, "code": "USD", "symbol": "$" },
    "display_rate": 0.021
  },
  "line_items": [
    {
      "item_id": 100,
      "variant_id": null,
      "unit_price": 150,
      "qty": 2,
      "line_total": 320,
      "display_unit_price": 3.15,
      "display_line_total": 6.72
    }
  ]
}
```
